"independent, untied, liberated, detached, his mind free of limits."

msgctxt "mn111:18.5"
msgid "So ‘atthi uttari nissaraṇan’ti pajānāti."
msgstr "He understood: ‘There is an escape beyond.’"

msgctxt "mn111:18.6"
msgid "Tabbahulīkārā atthitvevassa hoti. (8)"
msgstr "And by repeated practice he knew for sure that there is."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn111:19.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, sāriputto sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ "
"samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati. Paññāya cassa disvā "
"āsavā parikkhīṇā honti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor "
"non-perception, he entered and remained in the cessation of perception and "
"feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, his defilements came to an end."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
msgctxt "mn111:20.1"
msgid "So tāya samāpattiyā sato vuṭṭhahati."
msgstr "And he emerged from that attainment with mindfulness."

#. VAR: vuṭṭhahitvā ye dhammā → ye te dhammā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "mn111:20.2"
msgid ""
"So tāya samāpattiyā sato vuṭṭhahitvā ye dhammā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā te "
"dhamme samanupassati:"
msgstr ""
"Then he contemplated the phenomena in that attainment that had passed, "
"ceased, and perished:"

msgctxt "mn111:20.3"
msgid "‘evaṃ kirame dhammā ahutvā sambhonti, hutvā paṭiventī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘So it seems that these phenomena, not having been, come to be; and having "
"come to be, they flit away.’"

msgctxt "mn111:20.4"
msgid ""
"So tesu dhammesu anupāyo anapāyo anissito appaṭibaddho vippamutto visaṃyutto "
"vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati."
msgstr ""
"And he meditated without attraction or repulsion for those phenomena; "
"independent, untied, liberated, detached, his mind free of limits."

msgctxt "mn111:20.5"
msgid "So ‘natthi uttari nissaraṇan’ti pajānāti."
msgstr "He understood: ‘There is no escape beyond.’"

msgctxt "mn111:20.6"
msgid "Tabbahulīkārā natthi tvevassa hoti."
msgstr "And by repeated practice he knew for sure that there is not."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn111:21.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kho taṃ, bhikkhave, sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr "And if there’s anyone of whom it may be rightly said that"

msgctxt "mn111:21.2"
msgid ""
"‘vasippatto pāramippatto ariyasmiṃ sīlasmiṃ, vasippatto pāramippatto "
"ariyasmiṃ samādhismiṃ, vasippatto pāramippatto ariyāya paññāya, vasippatto "
"pāramippatto ariyāya vimuttiyā’ti, sāriputtameva taṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr ""
"they have attained mastery and perfection in noble ethics, immersion, "
"wisdom, and freedom, it’s Sāriputta."

msgctxt "mn111:21.3"
msgid ""
"‘vasippatto pāramippatto ariyasmiṃ sīlasmiṃ, vasippatto pāramippatto "
"ariyasmiṃ samādhismiṃ, vasippatto pāramippatto ariyāya paññāya, vasippatto "
"pāramippatto ariyāya vimuttiyā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya22"></a>
msgctxt "mn111:22.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kho taṃ, bhikkhave, sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr "And if there’s anyone of whom it may be rightly said that"

msgctxt "mn111:22.2"
msgid ""
"‘bhagavato putto oraso mukhato jāto dhammajo dhammanimmito dhammadāyādo no "
"āmisadāyādo’ti, sāriputtameva taṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr ""
"they’re the Buddha’s true-born child, born from his mouth, born of the "
"teaching, created by the teaching, heir to the teaching, not the heir in "
"material things, it’s Sāriputta."

msgctxt "mn111:22.3"
msgid ""
"‘bhagavato putto oraso mukhato jāto dhammajo dhammanimmito dhammadāyādo no "
"āmisadāyādo’ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya23"></a>
msgctxt "mn111:23.1"
msgid ""
"Sāriputto, bhikkhave, tathāgatena anuttaraṃ dhammacakkaṃ pavattitaṃ "
"sammadeva anuppavattetī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Sāriputta rightly keeps rolling the supreme Wheel of Dhamma that was rolled "
"forth by the Realized One.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn111:23.2"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn111:23.3"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn111:23.4"
msgid "Anupadasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
